title: '"4. We invite clients to notice that parts have “blended” with the Self, or we help parts notice that the Self will be available when they separate or “step back.” ... By the same token, the IFS therapist continually scans inside herself for blended parts and asks them to separate so she can return to Self-leadership."'
pid: 9efdea7b-9a8c-47e8-b04b-1b974c4b66c8
